text: Kharino () is a rural locality (a village) in Asovskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 16 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Kharino, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
